description: Pandamonium Doughnuts is an artisan, 'scratch' doughnut bakery and is in the business of creating handmade, specialty gourmet doughnuts with a unique twist and introducing these new, imaginative creations to Champaign-Urbana. These sweet treats include "yeast' and "cake" style doughnuts, and flavors can range from the decadent (Maple Bacon Apple Fritter) to the simply sweet (Raspberry Almond). Stop by and treat yourself to one of these delicious doughnuts today!
name: Pandamonium Doughnuts
